com.influxdb.query

Class FluxColumn

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.influxdb.query.FluxColumn

  • public final class FluxColumn
extends Object
    This class represents a column header specification of FluxTable.

    The mapping data types for a column are:

    • "boolean" to Boolean
    • "unsignedLong" to Long
    • "long" to Long
    • "double" to Double
    • "string" to String
    • "base64Binary" to bytes array
    • "dateTime:RFC3339" to Instant
    • "dateTime:RFC3339Nano" to Instant
    • "duration" to Duration
